post_text:
This Thursday, the community is invited to watch Powderpuff Football and Gorilla Volleyball. The Booster Club will provide a pancake supper. The Sophomore class will be serving. This will be a free meal, however, there will be a donation jar, with all money going to the Sophomore class.

Friday is Homecoming. Football begins at 3pm. The crowning of the queen and king will be at halftime. Volleyball will start at 5:30.

The Junior class will be serving pulled pork sandwich, corn, and cole slaw for $7. They will also have homemade pie. Yum!

It would be great to see a lot of blue and gold cheering on our teams.
